    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features a mid-mounted 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral exhaust note. The chassis maintains exceptional torsional rigidity, paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and fresh pads for the four-piston monobloc calipers. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a dedicated driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp, offering a neutral handling balance through every apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
