      "description": "This 2018 executive sport sedan is a remarkable example of pride of ownership. The exterior paint maintains a brilliant, deep luster, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use, while the body lines remain sharp and free of significant blemishes. Step inside to a cabin that feels truly premium; the leather upholstery is supple and well-conditioned, the dashboard is free of sun damage, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and recent fluid services. The ride is smooth and composed, with a suspension that handles corners with precision and tires that offer excellent tread life. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for a new owner who appreciates a well-cared-for machine that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 34500.0,
