      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home. This car has been super reliable for me and is still in solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver or a fun weekend cruiser. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road today! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
