    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the high-revving 3.6L M96 flat-six engine, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized power band. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by a precision-tuned multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts. Crucial preventive maintenance has been performed, including the installation of an upgraded IMS bearing and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring the mechanical longevity of the powertrain. The braking system remains sharp, featuring four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors for superior heat dissipation. This is a mechanically sound driver's car that balances raw performance with legendary Porsche engineering.",
